sometimes things suck.  on some occasions, there is not much you can do about it.  you just have to sit there and let it suck.
http://m2tigerz.livejournal.com/4284.html

We got ferrets! How fun is that?! There are two boys, one white and one black.  I named the white one cracker...you can guess what we were gonna name the black one but decided not to.  They are tons of fun to play with, and they're real squirly litte animals.  They hop all over the place, and they run into things a lot :-)

We (my boyf and I) have two lizards also, Tyrone and Tweak.  Tweak is mine, he's the cool one.  Tyrone used to be fun, but he's turned into a bitch and now I cant pick him up without getting clawed to death.
http://m2tigerz.livejournal.com/4046.html

Lets see.....

Spring Break was nice and relaxing- you won't be seeing me on college girls gone wild after this one.  Spent the whole week with my roommate at my grandma's house.  Got to shop, spend a couple days on the beach, tour Warner Bros. studios, go to Disneyland, and eat LOTS of sushi!!!!!

My friends and I found a duplex to live in thats right down the street where I work.  NO MORE SORORITY HOUSE!!!!  Not that I don't love the house...but it will be nice not to need a hotel room every time my boyfriend wants to visit, and sleepin in the car is no fun!

These past two weeks were awful!  I totally felt like I was falling apart.  In every class I have some major project goin on, and they all had due dates within the past week.  Add on all the stupid miniscule busy work assignments that I have, and it makes for total hell week.  I survived, barely.  Skipped a few classes here, a few chapters there...and went a couple days on only 3 hours of sleep.  Not fun!  I bought myself a new planner to get organized, that seemed to be my main problem.  If everything isnt where its supposed to be, I fall apart, plain and simple.  I'm already ready for this semester to be over with....then a few weeks after that I'll be 21!!!!  Bout damn time too.  It figures though, I'll finally be old enough to party with my friends, and all my older friends will be graduating and leaving.  

I got my tongue pierced!  Amazingly enough, it didnt hurt when I got it done.  However, its swelled bunches, so now I have issues with eating and talking.  Hopefully it will heal soon...its already been 3 days!

Hope everyone had a good Easter- I spent mine with my family and my boyfriend.  I got an easter egg :-)  Guess I'm too old for the full-out easter basket.

Its late now....bedtime...zzzzzzzzzzzzzzzz
http://m2tigerz.livejournal.com/3747.html

So I didn't think my boyfriend was the romantic type.  Apparently he's got it in him somewhere, its just a matter of getting it out.  I went home this past weekend to find 3 roses and a card sitting on the coffee table.  The card (of the way fun sexy type) directed me to go to the bedroom.  There, I found another 3 roses on the pillows, and the bed was covered in rose petals.  There was another couple of notes that directed me to his pile of stuffed animals (he's a fan of the claw machine).  In the pile was a cute, blue, fuzzy puppy that he bought for me, and hidden under the collar around its neck was a beautiful heart necklace with three little swooshes in the middle that have diamonds at the end of them.  It was the same necklace that I picked out from a valentine's day flyer we got from helzberg diamonds.  How cute and romantic is that?!?!
http://m2tigerz.livejournal.com/3446.html

You're Element is Night. You're a loner who is very
creative but never show your work to anyone.
You may smile a little but sadness or
loneliness surround you and other can feel it
when they're near you. You have a dark or
unusual beauty that makes you mysterious and
you probably have a lot of secrets that you've
never told anyone. You're beauty is intriging
and unorthidox but the real thing that makes
you special is your eyes. Something in them
makes them like "Diamonds in the
Rough."

You are a bronze dragon! You are the biggest of
the males, and generally you are the only one
who gets to mate with the queen. You are an
excellent leader. Your human partner is likely
to be a Wingleader or even Weyrleader, the
person in charge of the entire Weyr, and you
are the mate of the senior queen. You are
respected by the lower colors, and if you are
the Weyrleader's dragon you are always obeyed,
unless the queen contradicts you. Since queens
are relatively uncommon, you are widely
considered by humans the best dragon to be
paired with.

What color of Pernese dragon are you?
brought to you by Quizilla

I'm goin to Cali!!!! Spring Break in L.A. here I come :-)  I would like to thank all the members of my family out there- my grandparents, uncles, aunts- without them this trip would not be possible!

On a side note, it turns out I'm on my way to becoming a super senior.  I tried to get out in four years, I really did, but its just not gonna happen.  I have three semesters left (not counting this one) for those of you who are wondering.  I'll be student teaching in fall of '05 instead of spring '05.

You are a Khaos angel. You are different from all
the rest. You are a special breed of angel,
prone to suffer in the world that you are in
now. No matter how much you try to believe that
your not special, you are. There is alot that
you want to do in this world. Khaos angels are
very dramatic, we tend to have the ability to
cheer people up no matter what the mood, and
hold in your emotions. You should be proud,
Khaos angels are very rare to find in this
world of ours... (and yes. you are a completely
different type. Hence the name
"Khaos" and not Chaos. quite strange
huh?)

You are Form 1, Goddess: The Creator. "And The Goddess planted the acorn of life.
She cried a single tear and shed a single drop
of blood upon the earth where she buried it.
From her blood and tear, the acorn grew into
the world." Some examples of the Goddess Form are Gaia (Greek),
Jehova (Christian), and Brahma (Indian). The Goddess is associated with the concept of
creation, the number 1, and the element of
earth. Her sign is the dawn sun. As a member of Form 1, you are a charismatic
individual and people are drawn to you.
Although sometimes you may seem emotionally
distant, you are deeply in tune with other
people's feelings and have tremendous empathy.
Sometimes you have a tendency to neglect your
own self. Goddesses are the best friends to
have because they're always willing to help.

Which Mythological Form Are You?
brought to you by Quizilla

You're the pirate everyone else wants to throw in the ocean -- not to get rid of you, you understand; just to get rid of the smell. You can be a little bit unpredictable, but a pirate's life is far from full of certainties, so that fits in pretty well. Arr!

failed American dream. Although full of hate,

conscience of the City. Frightening thought,
but he's the only one we've got.
